I love this event so, so much. It‚Äôs amazing to get to see them just sit back, relax, and enjoy a fun game of league, especially after the high stakes of worlds. T1 being there brings so much weight to it, cause where else would teams like NNO and LR get to play the world champions, but the nemesis draft and the change of roles in the last game just made it even more awesome. Of course our T1 circus are down for whatever. Like, they were all cheesing all throughout the event. 
Also. That intro was the best thing I‚Äôve seen all year. Bass boosted Legends never die as the players walked out to a sea of hands with the T1 flag flying in the background? It felt like gods were walking into the arena. The kind of entrance this team and Faker should have literally everywhere, tbfh.
Thank you Red Bull, Caedrel, and everyone involved in making this a thing. See yall next year!
